Interface IClient

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BaseClient, LayoutClient, LogUnitClient, ManagementClient, SequencerClient

    public interface IClient
    This is an interface which all clients to a ClientRouter must implement. Created by mwei on 12/8/15.
